# Mark Javadoc as documentation
**/javadoc/** linguist-documentation
**/docs/** linguist-documentation

# Mark build outputs as generated
**/build/ linguist-generated
**/out/ linguist-generated
**/target/ linguist-generated

# Ignore IDE files
**/.idea/ linguist-vendored
**/*.iml linguist-vendored
**/.gradle/ linguist-vendored

# Ignore local properties
local.properties linguist-generated

# Mark HTML files as documentation
*.html linguist-documentation

# Mark JAR files as generated
*.jar linguist-generated

# Mark APK files as generated
*.apk linguist-generated
*.aab linguist-generated
